Class Identity

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.straas.android.sdk.authentication.identity.Identity
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Parcelable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Identity

    public class Identity
extends Object
implements Parcelable
    Identity represents a member.

    You could put member token in Identity(String) to get the Identity that represents the member.
